OL,5,G1845 FIFA World Cup 2026 Final
OL,6,     FSpain v Argentina (Kick-off
OL,7,     F8.00pm). Coverage of the final,
OL,8,     Fwhich takes place at New York/New
OL,9,     FJersey Stadium in the USA. Spain
OL,10,     Freached only their second World
OL,11,     FCup final by defeating tournament
OL,12,     Ffavourites France with a
OL,13,     Fmasterclass in their semi-final,
OL,14,     Fwinning 2-0 and completely
OL,15,     Fnullifying a disjointed French
OL,16,     Foutfit with ease. They won on
OL,17,     Ftheir only other appearance in the
OL,18,     Ffinal, against the Netherlands in
OL,19,     F2010, and start as favourites
OL,20,     Fagainst the defending champions.
OL,21,     FArgentina are aiming to become
OL,22,     Fonly the third nation in history
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
