OL,10,     Fin which the questions have
OL,11,     Fnothing to do with remembering
OL,12,     Ffacts, but are all about logic and
OL,13,     Fcommon sense. A hundred
OL,14,     Fcontestants begin every show, but
OL,15,     Fwho will make it to the end and
OL,16,     Fanswer a question only one per
OL,17,     Fcent of the country can get right
OL,18,     F- and win up to #100,000?
