OL,5,G0235 The Vardys
OL,6,     FDespite Jamie's best efforts on
OL,7,     Fthe pitch, his new Italian side
OL,8,     Fare struggling to get a win and
OL,9,     Fstay out of the relegation zone.
OL,10,     FThings go from bad to worse when
OL,11,     Fthe Vardys' lakeside villa is
OL,12,     Fdramatically burgled, leaving the
OL,13,     Fwhole family on edge and
OL,14,     Fconsidering whether to return
OL,15,     Fhome. On a whistle-stop trip back
OL,16,     Fto the UK, Becky and Jamie stage
OL,17,     Fan elaborate photoshoot but also
OL,18,     Ffind a quiet moment to make the
OL,19,     Fbig decision - whatever happens
OL,20,     Fwith the football, they will bring
OL,21,     Fthe kids home
